snippet.title: RACE KARTING LEGEND DAVE SERA AT TODD ROAD KART TRACK | Street Kart Racing Game
snippet.description:
Get the best racing game on mobile: https://apple.co/2WlEfxo

Take on Dave Sera and Win Dave's Helmet.

First look at the Street Kart Racing January 2020 Update:
- New Track: Todd Road, Melbourne Australia
- New Kart: Sera Kart

In this update:
- Take on Dave Sera in the 2020 Live Event - starts 5th February 2020
- Race against Dave in the final in his kart
- Same equipment. Same kit. Skill wins.

Join our community
www.facebook.com/groups/streetkartracing

Find out more:
www.streetkart.me
www.kartpfi.com
www.kartrepublic.com
www.rosbergracingacademy.com

Characters in the game include:
Dexter Patterson, Kai Askey, Patricija Stalidzane, Nico Rosberg, Marijn Kremers, SuperGT, Olin Galli, Olli Caldwell, Duncan Abbott, Dave Sera

About
Street Kart Racing is an independent racing project to create the most competitive racing game on mobile. Created by a couple of friends, Duncan and Ross who started building the game from a shed in 2012. They've come a long way since then but still have an unwavering focus to involve the SK community along the way.
